{
    "attributes": {
        "action": "Increase funding for Ambulance and A&E services to reduce waiting times",
        "additional_details": "I want the government in Parliament to do this, because I think at the moment the conditions in the NHS are bad; and I\u2019m pioneering for change. This is especially needed for the Northwest.",
        "background": "I want the government and Parliament to provide the NHS with more funding for A&E departments and ambulances so we can reduce care being provided in corridors. Also to improve the wages of staff as well as ambulance wait times.",
